1 (2) Eight percent on the value of liquor sold in licensed establishments as defined
2 in Title 28‑A, section 2, subsection 15, in accordance with Title 28‑A, chapter 43
3 and liquor sold for on-premises consumption by a licensed brewery, small brewery,
